race.comment: CHAINS OF LOVE (7) is another top-winning chance for the high-striking Messara-Gavranich stable. Made an encouraging debut narrowly beaten over 1100m at this track jumping even money. Led in that and can cross over and do the same. Fitter and can get off the mark. NOVAYA (1) made an encouraging debut missing by 0.9L at Port Macquarie. Draws low and the top hoop is a positive jockey engagement. Improver who has to be included. APADANA (11) debuts and impressed here at her latest trial. Reith sticks from all and the blinkers are on. She looks all set to race well. GRANDE DIABLO (4) debuts and placed the second of two trials. He should be around the mark.
